                <head>No. 501<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On October 21, the Majlis of Iran approved the government’s single article oil
                    bill by a vote of 113 in favor, 5 opposed, with 1 deputy abstaining. The bill,
                    however, also required Senate approval and, upon completion of the vote in the
                    Majlis, the government presented the measure to the Iranian Senate for its
                    consideration.</p>
            </div>
